article.story: LITTLE ROCK, Ark. -- — KJ Doucet scored 20 points as Winthrop beat Little Rock 85-68 on Sunday. Doucet added five rebounds for the Eagles (8-3). Alex Timmerman scored 15 points and added six rebounds. Kasen Harrison had 12 points and was 3 of 8 shooting and 6 of 7 from the free throw line. The Trojans (4-6) were led by Jaylen Crocker-Johnson, who posted 15 points, nine rebounds and two blocks. Bradley Douglas added 14 points for Little Rock. Jamir Chaplin also had 11 points and two blocks. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
